data.description: A captivating find in the sought-after Glenwood Park neighborhood! This charming 4 bed, 2 bath Cape Cod-style home offers the perfect blend of classic design and modern upgrades. As you step inside, the recessed lighting elegantly highlights the well-appointed living spaces. Cooking and entertaining in this space is an absolute delight with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. One of the highlights of this home is the sunroom located just off the kitchen. This bright and airy space effortlessly bridges indoor and outdoor living. And speaking of the outdoors, the spacious backyard is a true oasis. Complete with a shed and carport, it's both practical and picturesque, providing ample storage and a shaded area for your vehicles. Location couldn't be more ideal – close to the Naval Base, ODU, and a variety of shopping and dining options including the interstate. Back on the market, no fault to the seller. New water heater installed!
